  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 20th level, you are one with the storm. You gain&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/universal-monster-rules#TOC-Immunity-Ex-or-Su-\">immunity</a>&nbsp;to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Deafened\" rel=\"nofollow\">deafness</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Stunned\" rel=\"nofollow\">stunning</a>, and wind effects and gain&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Blindsight-and-Blindsense\">blindsight</a>&nbsp;120 feet against&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Concealment\">concealment</a>&nbsp;from natural or magical fog, mist, or weather. Once per day, when attacked with an electricity or sonic effect, you may forgo your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Saving-Throws\">saving throw</a>&nbsp;and absorb the energies of the attack, healing 1 point of damage for every 3 points of damage the attack would otherwise have dealt.</p>"
